name: Interoceanic Fiber Optic Artistic Interaction
description:
In a world that dreams of satellite telecommunications, even today 99% of these are done by means of interoceanic cables that cross the world in the depths of the oceans.
In this GIF is represented in an imaginary way, the communication flow through one of them, between the bots that made these images and that are part of the first two series, "001" and "Follow the dance of Pandora Panama - Portraits", from the "Deconstruction" Collection.
